**[MEDIUM] `stats_models/src/lib.rs`:Line 115 – Inefficient matrix creation from slice.**
The `Lm::fit` function creates `faer::Mat` instances using `Mat::from_fn`, which involves a closure call for every element. This is less efficient than creating a matrix view directly from the input slice and then converting it to an owned matrix.

